The '''Sixteenth Tactical Recon Group''' was a section of the [[New Republic Fifth Fleet|Fifth Battle Group]] of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]] during the [[Black Fleet Crisis]].

Because at that time the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] was losing its reconnaissance craft, useful intelligence on the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]] was in short supply. The 16th was formed to fill the gap. Its mission, under the command of [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Mauit'ta]], was to scout the cluster &mdash; with particular focus on [[Yevetha]]n movements, deployments and facilities. To accomplish this, it was given a full complement of [[Droid/Legends|droid]]-controlled [[Ferret-class reconnaissance vessel|''Ferret''-class drones]] and the larger, crewed [[Prowler-class reconnaissance vessel|''Prowler''-class reconnaissance craft]].

